---
import BaseLayout from '../components/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="页面不存在 | 刘强的博客" description="你访问的页面不存在">
  <section class="container panel not-found">
    <span class="eyebrow">404</span>
    <h1>这页似乎已经离开了当前路径</h1>
    <p>你可以回到首页继续浏览，或者直接使用站内搜索查找文章与项目。</p>
    <div class="actions">
      <a class="button button-primary" href="/">返回首页</a>
      <a class="button button-secondary" href="/search">去搜索</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .not-found {
    display: grid;
    gap: 18px;
    padding: 42px;
    margin-top: 24px;
  }

  .not-found h1 {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.2rem);
  }

  .not-found p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--text-soft);
    line-height: 1.9;
  }

  .actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 12px;
  }
</style>
